<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>My Web Page</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/login.css">
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" defer></script>
    </head>
    <body class="text-center vsc-initialized">
        <div class="container col-xl-10 col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
            <div class="row align-items-center g-lg-5 py-5">
              <div class="col-lg-7 text-center text-lg-start">
                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold lh-1 text-body-emphasis mb-3">Welcome to SportsCentral!</h1>
                <p>Welcome to SportsCentral, your go-to destination for all things sports! Ignite your passion, connect with fellow athletes, and discover thrilling sporting eventsâ€”all in one place.</p>
                <p>Unleash your sporting potential with SportsCentral's streamlined interface. With just a few clicks, you can explore a wide range of activities and easily book your favorite sports experiences. From courts to fields, we've got you covered.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-10 mx-auto col-lg-5">
                <form action="/login" method="post" class="p-md-5 border rounded-3 bg-body-tertiary">
                  <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert"><%= errorMsg %></div>
                  <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" name="email" id="floatingInput" placeholder="name@example.com">
                    <label for="floatingInput">Email</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="floatingPassword" placeholder="Password" name="password">
                    <label for="floatingPassword">Password</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox mb-3">
                    <label>
                      <input type="checkbox" value="remember-me"> Remember me
                    </label><br>
                    <a href="\register" name="register">Don't have an account?</a>
                  </div>
                  <button class="w-100 btn btn-lg btn-dark" type="submit" name="signin">Sign in</button>
                  <hr class="my-4">
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
    </body>
</html>
